<item>
            <title>[FLINK-12075] Not able to submit jobs on YARN when there&apos;s a firewall</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-12075</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If there is a firewall around the YARN cluster and the machine, submitting&#160;flink job it is unpractical because new flink clusters start up with random ports for REST communication.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-5758&quot; title=&quot;Port-range for the web interface via YARN&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-5758&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-5758&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&#160;should&apos;ve fixed this. But it seems &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-11081&quot; title=&quot;Support binding port range for REST server&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-11081&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-11081&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; either undid the changes or did not implement this. The relevant code is changed in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-11081&quot; title=&quot;Support binding port range for REST server&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-11081&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-11081&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/commit/730eed71ef3f718d61f85d5e94b1060844ca56db#diff-487838863ab693af7008f04cb3359be3R102&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/commit/730eed71ef3f718d61f85d5e94b1060844ca56db#diff-487838863ab693af7008f04cb3359be3R102&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
